input: The cat is green. The cat sees the dog. The cat visits the dog. The dog eats the mouse. The dog is young. The dog sees the tiger. The dog visits the cat. The dog visits the mouse. The mouse sees the dog. The mouse visits the cat. The mouse visits the dog. The tiger eats the cat. The tiger is nice. The tiger sees the dog. The tiger sees the mouse. The tiger visits the dog. If someone eats the mouse then they are green. If someone is young and they see the dog then they are green. If someone eats the dog then they see the dog. If the tiger eats the dog and the dog visits the mouse then the tiger is young. If someone visits the cat and the cat is nice then the cat sees the dog. If someone sees the dog and the dog is green then they see the cat. If someone is rough then they eat the dog. All green people are rough. If someone eats the dog then the dog visits the mouse. Question: The dog sees the cat.?
output:
universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Cat : obj
constant Dog : obj
constant Mouse : obj
constant Tiger : obj

constant Green : obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Visits : obj → obj → Prop
constant Eats : obj → obj → Prop
constant Young : obj → Prop
constant Nice : obj → Prop
constant Rough : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Green Cat
axiom T2 : Sees Cat Dog
axiom T3 : Visits Cat Dog
axiom T4 : Eats Dog Mouse
axiom T5 : Young Dog
axiom T6 : Sees Dog Tiger
axiom T7 : Visits Dog Cat
axiom T8 : Visits Dog Mouse
axiom T9 : Sees Mouse Dog
axiom T10 : Visits Mouse Cat
axiom T11 : Visits Mouse Dog
axiom T12 : Eats Tiger Cat
axiom T13 : Nice Tiger
axiom T14 : Sees Tiger Dog
axiom T15 : Sees Tiger Mouse
axiom T16 : Visits Tiger Dog

axiom R1 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Mouse → Green x
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Young x ∧ Sees x Dog → Green x
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Dog → Sees x Dog
axiom R4 : Eats Tiger Dog ∧ Visits Dog Mouse → Young Tiger
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Cat ∧ Nice Cat → Sees Cat Dog
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Dog ∧ Green Dog → Sees x Cat
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Rough x → Eats x Dog
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Green x → Rough x
axiom R9 : ∀ x : obj, Eats x Dog → Visits Dog Mouse

theorem dog_sees_cat : Sees Dog Cat :=
begin
  apply R6,
  split,
  exact T6,
  apply R2,
  split,
  exact T5,
  exact T6,
end

-- The answer is True
